# API Controllers & DTOs

Follow `docs/API_STANDARDS.md`.

## Must

- `/v1` prefix; declare permissions on routes.
- Validate input at the edge; reject unexpected fields where feasible.
- Success `{ data, meta }`; errors as problem+json with `correlationId` + stable `code`.
- Idempotency-Key on leave apply/cancel and similar mutating POSTs.
- Map domain errors in a central filter — no stack traces to clients.

## Never

Business rules in controllers · unbounded list endpoints · 200 OK with error strings as the only signal.
